layers.nm: In this scenario, the A.I has detected all ‘moving automobiles’ and has decided to run into them to show its danger. However, it did not know that these humans will cease to exist when their ‘vehicle’ is hit.

layers.nm: A.I. self-driving cars detect elements of the environment by locating shapes through their short and long range optical cameras. These shapes are then segmented and catagorised in order to identify what the object encountered is.
